<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/wiki/Marlin_K._Jensen" title="Marlin K. Jensen">Marlin K. Jensen</a>, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/ensign/1994/10/a-union-of-love-and-understanding?lang=eng">"A Union of Love and Understanding"</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/Ensign_(LDS_magazine)" title="Ensign (LDS magazine)">Ensign</a></i>, October 1994.</span>
